nodes.text: Gen-6 was a starship that was produced during the Separatist Crisis.

In 25 BBY, the Typha-Dors loaned a Gen-6 to Jedi Knight Obi-Wan Kenobi and his Padawan Anakin Skywalker in their hunt for the scientist Jenna Zan Arbor after they had helped to avert a planetary invasion by the Vanqor fleet.
